_sText:
Hooray, my second map. I wish I could have selected more than on category, however i thought a fight yard would be appropriate. This map would also fit under the fun or gun game categories. This is a fast pased map based out of midevil times, complete with castles, moats, and drawbridge! This will be fun for any DM GG or FY server. Download and enjoy!

P.S. dont fall in the moat!!
